<i>noun</i>: 환기 [환ː기], 자각 [자각], 각성 [각썽] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>환기 [환ː기]</dt><br>
<dd>arousal; awakening; stirring up</dd><br>
<dd>주의나 여론, 생각 등을 불러일으킴.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of bringing a person's attention to a certain matter, or stirring up public opinion, thought, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>자각 [자각]</dt><br>
<dd>self-consciousness; awakening</dd><br>
<dd>자기의 입장이나 능력 등을 스스로 느끼거나 깨달음.</dd><br>
<dd>Becoming aware of or realizing own position, situation, ability, etc.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>각성 [각썽]</dt><br>
<dd>1. awakening; coming to one's sense</dd><br>
<dd>잃었던 의식을 되찾거나 정신을 차림.</dd><br>
<dd>A state in which one recovers one's consciousness or becomes alert and awake.</dd><br>
<dd>2. awakening; realization</dd><br>
<dd>바르게 깨달아 앎.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of realize and understand something correctly.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>